query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.projectNumber, COUNT(a.id) as asset_count, 
       SUM(a.replacementValue) as total_replacement_value,
       AVG(a.fciScore) as avg_fci
FROM projects p 
LEFT JOIN assets a ON a.projectId = p.id 
WHERE p.id = 14 
GROUP BY p.id
